data.text:
Welcome to Catherine McAuley

Welcome to Catherine McAuley Primary School, a vibrant learning community where inclusivity and holistic child development are at the heart of our ethos.

At Catherine McAuley, we believe every child deserves an environment that is inclusive, focused on the development of the whole child, offers an educational program that is rigorous and challenging and actively supports wellbeing. When you join us at Catherine McAuley, you join the McAuley Family.

Our school is equipped with contemporary learning spaces, where our experienced educators facilitate engaging lessons tailored to each student's individual needs. We understand that learning extends beyond the classroom, which is why we offer a diverse range of extracurricular activities to foster a well-rounded education.

At Catherine McAuley, we place great emphasis on the wellbeing of our students. Our staff are committed to building strong relationships with every child, ensuring they feel supported and valued in their learning journey.

Join us at Catherine McAuley Primary School, where your child's educational journey will be nurtured and celebrated.
